Class PreDepthProcessor

java.lang.Object
com.jme3.post.PreDepthProcessor
All Implemented Interfaces:
SceneProcessor
public class PreDepthProcessor extends Object implements SceneProcessor
Processor that lays depth first, this can improve performance in complex scenes.
